Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:11.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:15.33,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仅为这理由而束缚
